<font class="content" color="#505050"><a href=http://www.darkrainguild.org/modules.php?op=modload&name=Forum&file=viewtopic&topic=36&forum=15&2>See what Halia wrote in the forums!</a><br><br> 
WOOT For the third night in a row, the General has fallen to Dark Rain forces.  He drops some nice weapon, I hear tell, BUT I can't find the stats on it :p - just trust me, it must be a nice one to have our warriors dragging us up there every evening ;)
The usual suspects were present: Keniden, Aaminah, Narchost, Bustyn, Stylez (played by Eldrynn - please note the change in your program), Bemeni, Ivanstab, Jehm, Jehm's annoying pet, and Sfortz (who couldn't stay connected last night). No Deaths! Nice Job Dark Rain! <img src=http://communities.msn.com/_Secure/0KwDqCn4NwQuAV8jGJyzBjLMi9OtfO67GTilh!tB8acRmd8doc0cQqEnSylkpyraJO*14VjZRnZQ/EQ000010.bmp>
