<font class="content" color="#505050">What an incredible weekend Dark Rain had! In addition to Kael and Fungus Grove, Minah killed Bergurgle on Saturday to get her epic started! WOOT! Even after all that excitement, when Brede said on Sunday &#8220; The guy in EW is up for the Coldain Ring quest!&#8221; , several of us got over to Velious as fast as we could. Brede, Bemeni, Trystyn, Jasdin, Mikaila, Calain, Narchost, Binabink, and new friend Tanean all helped during the day to get Brede finished with Ring 7! Next for him is the battle between the dorfs and the giants at the Ry&#8217;Gorr fort. As If that wasn&#8217;t enough , several of our members answered the call on an open raid on General V&#8217;Ghera in order to obtain rogue epic pieces for several rogues, including our own Ivanstab. Reports I hear of the battles were great! Dark Rain looked awesome! Good Job Guys! And Gratz to everyone this weekend &#8211; way to go Dark Rain! <br><br> Don&#8217;t Forget! <h2>Monthly Guild Meeting for all Members is Thursday, 9pm EST at the DL rings </h2>
 
