<font class="content" color="#505050">Saturday Night we went to Fungus Grove, gave Caller Groo some beer, and he <a href=http://www.allakhazam.com/db/quest.html?quest=1570>Summoned Beasties</a> for us all night long. It took us a couple cycles to figure out what the heck we were doing, but once we got it, it was the most fun I have had in a long time. Caller Groo became our best bud!  We got a little behind in the cycles, Groo kept calling, everyone was OOM and Low on Health, but since Groo was aggroed, we couldn't get him to stop! (Well, us dieing stopped him :P) After the CR,<br> 
Hals and Corri came in and it became almost easy :) No Rent Pods of Blue and Green Fungus were dropping to help mana<br> and health regen, PLUS Bemeni and Ivanstab each got a new <a href=http://www.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=7734>poker</a>, and our guest Crashbomba got a new <a href=http://www.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=8080>spear</a>!  A Great time was had by all! In attendance were: Brede, Bustyn, Sfortz, Clemm, Wandaln, Drydin, Ivanstab, Halia, Corriana, Otiss, Jehm,
 <br>Mikaila from Dark Rain and Friends Eldrynn, Crashbomba, Caliniel, Altiare, Gregel, and Thoraxen!
