<font class="content" color="#505050">Our first Taskmaster Event was a success! Halia took us through Kael  - we cleared the bank no problem! We had two groups and it was just enough to get the job done - unfortunately, they couldn't go as far as they would have liked, but Hal plans to take us back each Friday night, so we will get further and further each time ;)<br>
<br>
Last night in Attendance Were:<br>
Bustyn, Brede, Keniden, Halia, Minah, Ivanstab, Bemeni, Jehm, PLUS we had friends from Epic Raiders and Phirren all join us!
